OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783923682
OL,3,CMore French border guards deployed in
OL,4,CUK to reduce delays
OL,6,FMore French border guards have been
OL,7,Fdeployed to checkpoints in Britain to
OL,8,Fprevent technology failures from
OL,9,Fcausing long delays for travellers
OL,10,Fthis summer.
OL,12,FBritain pushed for the larger French
OL,13,Fpresence at EU border checks amid
OL,14,Ffears of delays caused by the bloc's
OL,15,Fnew Entry/Exit System (EES).
OL,17,FThe new EES checks require travellers
OL,18,Fto give biometric data, fingerprints
OL,19,Fand facial scans, as well as
OL,20,Fregistering their passport, when they
OL,21,Ftravel to Europe for the first time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
