OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783923682
OL,3,CMore French border guards deployed in
OL,4,CUK to reduce delays
OL,6,FAfter that, the digital border system
OL,7,Fshould allow travellers to enter and
OL,8,Fexit Europe with only a facial scan
OL,9,Ffor up to three years.
OL,11,FBut many border points are reportedly
OL,12,Fcollecting the same initial scans
OL,13,Fmultiple times.
OL,15,FThe system has caused delays in
OL,16,Fairports, and at borders where there
OL,17,Fare French checkpoints on UK soil,
OL,18,Flike at the Port of Dover.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
