OL,3,CMore French border guards deployed in
OL,4,CUK to reduce delays
OL,6,FThe Police Aux Frontieres have
OL,7,Fdeployed more staff to UK-based
OL,8,Fcheckpoints to manually register those
OL,9,Fleaving for France.
OL,11,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,12,Fbrokered the agreement for the
OL,13,Fincreased presence with her French
OL,14,Fcounterpart Phillippe Tabarot, ahead
OL,15,Fof the summer holidays.
OL,17,FThis extra presence will be in place
OL,18,Fwhile the French border force awaits
OL,19,Fthe installation of new passport
OL,20,Fbooths and tablets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
