OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783923682
OL,3,CMore French border guards deployed in
OL,4,CUK to reduce delays
OL,6,FMinisters have announced they will
OL,7,Fprovide #20 million of funding to
OL,8,Fincrease the number of booths, on top
OL,9,Fof #10.5m they have already put
OL,10,Ftowards preventing disruption.
OL,12,FMs Alexander said: "Everyone deserves
OL,13,Fto enjoy their summer holiday without
OL,14,Fdelays ` which is why we are doing all
OL,15,Fwe can to help travellers get through
OL,16,Fthese new EU security checks as
OL,17,Fsmoothly as possible.
OL,26,@tD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
