OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1783923682
OL,3,CMore French border guards deployed in
OL,4,CUK to reduce delays
OL,6,F"As well as the over #20 million we
OL,7,Fhave given to increase booths for
OL,8,Fpassport checks and minimise
OL,9,Fdisruption, I have raised
OL,10,Fholidaymakers' concerns directly with
OL,11,Fthe EU commissioner for transport to
OL,12,Fmake sure they are playing their part
OL,13,Fto reduce delays during the busiest
OL,14,Ftravel period of the year.
OL,16,F"I will do everything in my power to
OL,17,Fhelp holidaymakers on their way."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOUyD@aO]
